{{!
    @template mod_simplelesson/attempt_row
    Moodle table row rendering template for student attempt data

    Context variables required for this template:
    * firstname string user/respondent firstname
    * lastname string user/respondent firstname
    * datetaken string with date information - formatted
    * status string status of the attempt (complete/incomplete)
    * sessionscore string from the Moodle question table
    * maxscore int the total mark available for the question
    * timetaken int the number of seconds taken in answering the question


    Example context (json):
        {
         "firstname": "Fred",
         "Lastname": "Flintstone",
         "datetaken": "1970-1-1 12:00",
         "status": "Complete",
         "sessionscore": "10",
         "maxscore": "10",
         "timetaken": "1"
        }
}}
<tr class="danger">
  <td>{{firstname}}</td>
  <td>{{lastname}}</td>
  <td>{{datetaken}}</td>
  <td>{{status}}</td>
  <td>{{sessionscore}}</td>
  <td>{{maxscore}}</td>
  <td>{{timetaken}}</td>
</tr>